56static int
57smb_rap_parserqparam(const char *s, char **next, int *rlen)
58{
59 char *np;
60 int len;
61
62 switch (*s++) {
63 case 'L':
64 case 'T':
65 case 'W':
66 len = 2;
67 break;
68 case 'D':
69 case 'O':
70 len = 4;
71 break;
72 case 'b':
73 case 'F':
74 len = 1;
75 break;
76 case 'r':
77 case 's':
78 len = 0;
79 break;
80 default:
81 return EINVAL;
82 }
83 if (isdigit((unsigned char)*s)) {
84 len *= strtoul(s, &np, 10);
85 s = np;
86 }
87 *rlen = len;
88 memcpy(next, &s, sizeof(s));
89 return 0;
90}
91
92static int
93smb_rap_parserpparam(const char *s, char **next, int *rlen)
94{
95 char *np;
96 int len;
97
98 switch (*s++) {
99 case 'e':
100 case 'h':
101 len = 2;
102 break;
103 case 'i':
104 len = 4;
105 break;
106 case 'g':
107 len = 1;
108 break;
109 default:
110 return EINVAL;
111 }
112 if (isdigit((unsigned char)*s)) {
113 len *= strtoul(s, &np, 10);
114 s = np;
115 }
116 *rlen = len;
117 memcpy(next, &s, sizeof(s));
118 return 0;
119}
120
121static int
122smb_rap_parserpdata(const char *s, char **next, int *rlen)
123{
124 char *np;
125 int len;
126
127 switch (*s++) {
128 case 'B':
129 len = 1;
130 break;
131 case 'W':
132 len = 2;
133 break;
134 case 'D':
135 case 'O':
136 case 'z':
137 len = 4;
138 break;
139 default:
140 return EINVAL;
141 }
142 if (isdigit((unsigned char)*s)) {
143 len *= strtoul(s, &np, 10);
144 s = np;
145 }
146 *rlen = len;
147 memcpy(next, &s, sizeof(s));
148 return 0;
149}
150
151static int
152smb_rap_rqparam_z(struct smb_rap *rap, const char *value)
153{
154 int len = strlen(value) + 1;
155
156 bcopy(value, rap->r_npbuf, len);
157 rap->r_npbuf += len;
158 rap->r_plen += len;
159 return 0;
160}
161
162static int
163smb_rap_rqparam(struct smb_rap *rap, char ptype, char plen, long value)
164{
165 char *p = rap->r_npbuf;
166 int len;
167
168 switch (ptype) {
169 case 'L':
170 case 'W':
171 setwle(p, 0, value);
172 len = 2;
173 break;
174 case 'D':
175 setdle(p, 0, value);
176 len = 4;
177 break;
178 case 'b':
179 memset(p, value, plen);
180 len = plen;
181 default:
182 return EINVAL;
183 }
184 rap->r_npbuf += len;
185 rap->r_plen += len;
186 return 0;
187}
188
189int
190smb_rap_create(int fn, const char *param, const char *data,
191 struct smb_rap **rapp)
192{
193 struct smb_rap *rap;
194 char *p;
195 int plen, len;
196
197 rap = malloc(sizeof(*rap));
198 if (rap == NULL)
199 return 0;
200 bzero(rap, sizeof(*rap));
201 p = rap->r_sparam = rap->r_nparam = strdup(param);
202 rap->r_sdata = rap->r_ndata = strdup(data);
203 /*
204 * Calculate length of request parameter block
205 */
206 len = 2 + strlen(param) + 1 + strlen(data) + 1;
207
208 while (*p) {
209 if (smb_rap_parserqparam(p, &p, &plen) != 0)
210 break;
211 len += plen;
212 }
213 rap->r_pbuf = rap->r_npbuf = malloc(len);
214 smb_rap_rqparam(rap, 'W', 1, fn);
215 smb_rap_rqparam_z(rap, rap->r_sparam);
216 smb_rap_rqparam_z(rap, rap->r_sdata);
217 *rapp = rap;
218 return 0;
219}
220
221void
222smb_rap_done(struct smb_rap *rap)
223{
224 if (rap->r_sparam)
225 free(rap->r_sparam);
226 if (rap->r_sdata)
227 free(rap->r_sdata);
228 free(rap);
229}
230
231int
232smb_rap_setNparam(struct smb_rap *rap, long value)
233{
234 char *p = rap->r_nparam;
235 char ptype = *p;
236 int error, plen;
237
238 error = smb_rap_parserqparam(p, &p, &plen);
239 if (error)
240 return error;
241 switch (ptype) {
242 case 'L':
243 rap->r_rcvbuflen = value;
244 /* FALLTHROUGH */
245 case 'W':
246 case 'D':
247 case 'b':
248 error = smb_rap_rqparam(rap, ptype, plen, value);
249 break;
250 default:
251 return EINVAL;
252 }
253 rap->r_nparam = p;
254 return 0;
255}
256
257int
258smb_rap_setPparam(struct smb_rap *rap, void *value)
259{
260 char *p = rap->r_nparam;
261 char ptype = *p;
262 int error, plen;
263
264 error = smb_rap_parserqparam(p, &p, &plen);
265 if (error)
266 return error;
267 switch (ptype) {
268 case 'r':
269 rap->r_rcvbuf = value;
270 break;
271 default:
272 return EINVAL;
273 }
274 rap->r_nparam = p;
275 return 0;
276}
277
278static int
279smb_rap_getNparam(struct smb_rap *rap, long *value)
280{
281 char *p = rap->r_nparam;
282 char ptype = *p;
283 int error, plen = 0; /* XXX: gcc */
284
285 error = smb_rap_parserpparam(p, &p, &plen);
286 if (error)
287 return error;
288 switch (ptype) {
289 case 'h':
290 *value = ntohs(*(u_int16_t*)rap->r_npbuf);
291 break;
292 default:
293 return EINVAL;
294 }
295 rap->r_npbuf += plen;
296 rap->r_nparam = p;
297 return 0;
298}
299
300int
301smb_rap_request(struct smb_rap *rap, struct smb_ctx *ctx)
302{
303 u_int16_t *rp, conv;
304 u_int32_t *p32;
305 char *dp, *p = rap->r_nparam;
306 char ptype;
307 int error, rdatacnt, rparamcnt, entries, done, dlen;
308
309 rdatacnt = rap->r_rcvbuflen;
310 rparamcnt = rap->r_plen;
311 error = smb_t2_request(ctx, 0, 0, "\\PIPE\\LANMAN",
312 rap->r_plen, rap->r_pbuf, /* int tparamcnt, void *tparam */
313 0, NULL, /* int tdatacnt, void *tdata */
314 &rparamcnt, rap->r_pbuf, /* rparamcnt, void *rparam */
315 &rdatacnt, rap->r_rcvbuf /* int *rdatacnt, void *rdata */
316 );
317 if (error)
318 return error;
319 rp = (u_int16_t*)rap->r_pbuf;
320 rap->r_result = le16toh(*rp++);
321 conv = le16toh(*rp++);
322 rap->r_npbuf = (char*)rp;
323 rap->r_entries = entries = 0;
324 done = 0;
325 while (!done && *p) {
326 ptype = *p;
327 switch (ptype) {
328 case 'e':
329 rap->r_entries = entries = le16toh(*(u_int16_t*)rap->r_npbuf);
330 rap->r_npbuf += 2;
331 p++;
332 break;
333 default:
334 done = 1;
335 }
336/* error = smb_rap_parserpparam(p, &p, &plen);
337 if (error) {
338 smb_error("reply parameter mismath %s", 0, p);
339 return EBADRPC;
340 }*/
341 }
342 rap->r_nparam = p;
343 /*
344 * In general, unpacking entries we may need to relocate
345 * entries for proper alingning. For now use them as is.
346 */
347 dp = rap->r_rcvbuf;
348 while (entries--) {
349 p = rap->r_sdata;
350 while (*p) {
351 ptype = *p;
352 error = smb_rap_parserpdata(p, &p, &dlen);
353 if (error) {
354 smb_error("reply data mismath %s", 0, p);
355 return EBADRPC;
356 }
357 switch (ptype) {
358 case 'z':
359 p32 = (u_int32_t*)dp;
360 *p32 = (*p32 & 0xffff) - conv;
361 break;
362 }
363 dp += dlen;
364 }
365 }
366 return error;
367}
368
369int
370smb_rap_error(struct smb_rap *rap, int error)
371{
372 if (error)
373 return error;
374 if (rap->r_result == 0)
375 return 0;
376 return rap->r_result | SMB_RAP_ERROR;
377}
378
379int
380smb_rap_NetShareEnum(struct smb_ctx *ctx, int sLevel, void *pbBuffer,
381 int cbBuffer, int *pcEntriesRead, int *pcTotalAvail)
382{
383 struct smb_rap *rap;
384 long lval;
385 int error;
386
387 lval = -1; /* XXX gcc */
388 error = smb_rap_create(0, "WrLeh", "B13BWz", &rap);
389 if (error)
390 return error;
391 smb_rap_setNparam(rap, sLevel); /* W - sLevel */
392 smb_rap_setPparam(rap, pbBuffer); /* r - pbBuffer */
393 smb_rap_setNparam(rap, cbBuffer); /* L - cbBuffer */
394 error = smb_rap_request(rap, ctx);
395 if (error == 0) {
396 *pcEntriesRead = rap->r_entries;
397 error = smb_rap_getNparam(rap, &lval);
398 *pcTotalAvail = lval;
399 }
400 error = smb_rap_error(rap, error);
401 smb_rap_done(rap);
402 return error;
403}
